												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/bergwiseman/">Anastasia Berg and Rachel Wiseman</a></h6>
													<strong>Anastasia Berg</strong> is an Assistant Professor of Philosophy at the University of California, Irvine. She is an editor of <em>The Point</em>, and her writing has appeared in <em>The New York Times</em>​, <em>The Atlantic</em>, <em>The TLS</em>, <em>The Los Angeles Review of Books</em>, and <em>The Chronicle of Higher Education</em>.
